a)	New equipment from the supplier shall enter service in the hire industry in accordance with 1.2.1;
b)	The hirer has the responsibility to ensure that hired equipment complies with the requirements of this standard at the commencement of hire;
c)	Hirers may combine the function of the tag specified in 2.5.2.1 and their in-house 'Ready for
hire' tag.
